Install a Ruby version:

    https://github.com/asdf-vm/asdf-ruby
    https://github.com/rbenv/ruby-build/wiki#troubleshooting

    brew install rbenv/tap/openssl@1.0
    RUBY_CONFIGURE_OPTS="--with-openssl-dir=$(brew --prefix openssl@1.0)" asdf install ruby 2.3.8

Erlang

    KERL_CONFIGURE_OPTIONS="--without-javac --with-ssl=$(brew --prefix openssl)"  asdf install erlang 22.3.4
